{
  "stem": "20089.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went through to the dormitories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was horrified at the amount of stale bread that we found in the cupboard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also, the cupboards were dirty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They weren't clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when I think about it, bread was the-- was the survival kit that a lot of these people had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If they had bread, they could survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when they left the dining halls in the-- in the displaced persons camp, they always took a few slices of bread with them just in case they wouldn't be able to get bread again.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was really-- it wasn't necessary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would get bread again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think that their experience with such that one always needed that extra piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was disgusted that-- that the cupboards were dirty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what would the American senators say if they looked in the cupboards and they saw how dirty everything was?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But behind it all, of course, was the Jewish Agency.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want the camps to look clean, and hygienic, and-- and well laid out, because the Americans would then go back and say, yes, we must take these people out of sympathy.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and so they would send in a very, very positive report.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, then more immigrants would get to America than to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jewish Agency sabotaged our plan of cleanliness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And instead of making the place look clean and-- and very beautiful for the American congressmen, they made it look shabby, and dirty, and-- and unfavorable.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in fact, they even brought in animals from the German countryside to show what sort of people these Poles were, that they were ready to live with animals.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, of course, behind it all was Abram and the Jewish Agency.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
